rest_of_day_open: I think the rest of the week will go well. I'm hopeful for the future because I'm waiting to hear back on my job search. I'm looking forward to trying out a new video game. I feel motivated to try to get some exercise because I've been sitting still for too long.
critical_positive: I think one thing that worked well about the conversation is that we both had the intent to have a conversation for 25min and therefore were both interested in keeping the conversation going. I think we both had equal chances to speak though I spoke less just because that's the way I am. They were a very kind person as well.
critical_negative: I think one thing that didn't work as well is we didn't have a lot in common overall. But that was kind of negated by the fact that we were both interested in hearing what the other person had to say and learning more about them so it didn't matter. One result of that though is I think it makes the conversation more surface level which isn't a bad thing since that's expected in a conversation between strangers.
